latestPosts.caption:
✨The next time a brand asks to repost your content for free… don’t panic. Do *this* instead:

Let them repost *once* as a courtesy — but set clear boundaries (organic social *only,* no retailers or websites, and make sure they tag you!). Then, use it as an opportunity to pitch yourself for a *paid* partnership.

💼 Ask for the right contact.

📩 Send over your media kit and 2–3 creative content ideas.

📊 Bonus: include a branded proposal.

🔁 And follow up — seriously.

This method has helped me and the creators I work with land paid deals *time and time again.*

Save this for the next time it happens 💌

#InfluencerTips #ContentCreatorStrategy

aspiring content creators and influencerssss listen up! KNOW these things before you start taking your career full/time as an influencer:

✨genuinely love and enjoy creating content— FOR FREE!
✨get clear on your ‘why’ (your reason why you want to share your content on social media)
✨get out of your head, and support your delulu mindset 

this career may not be for you…and that’s okay! 

you may find that this is not the career may not be for you…and that’s okay! #influencermentor #creatormentor #influencertips

It’s not just unethical, it’s illegal! 🚨 

Disclose your content, period. #influencertips #influencermentor

latestPosts.caption:
I’ve been in my feelings about spending Valentine’s Day solo. 

To love myself, I’ll be cooking my fave meal, watching the new season of love is blind, and cuddling with my pup Olive 🐾

How are you spending it? 💕

January was… chaotic, but these products made life a little easier!

✨ @summerfridays Jet Lag Serum — lightweight hydration for everyday
✨ @lauramercier Natural Dewy Tinted Moisturizer — filter vibes IRL
✨ @summerfridays Lip Oil in Rosewood Nights — almost empty because it’s THAT good
✨ @firstaidbeauty Facial Radiance Pads & @thayersofficial Blemish Clearing Pads — breakout heroes
✨ @youthtothepeople Superberry Hydrate & Glow Dream Body Butter — longest-lasting body cream ever!
✨ @givenchybeauty L’INTERDIT ROUGE ULTIME — sexy, subtle, and always compliment-worthy

sooo what does this mean?👀

Not quite my $10K/month goal, but I’m still proud! Shoutout to my parents for helping with rent and utilities this month 🙏 and my amazing bookeeper (@honeydigit )who’s been managing my books since 2023! 

Here’s to earning more and spending smarter in February! Let me know what questions you have for next month’s breakdown 👀
